Textures
--------
The following planet textures were based on images from JPL, although most
have undergone alteration by myself. These images are essentially copyright
free as stated by JPL in their image use policy.
http://www.jpl.nasa.gov/imagepolicy/

"Courtesy NASA/JPL-Caltech."
Mercury
Venus
Jupiter
Saturn
Neptune
Pluto

The earth textures are public domain and obtained from:
http://www.shadedrelief.com

All other textures were created by me and are public domain.
